name: Magic Beans
directions: Straight back as you enter and to your right down a short hallway, then a quick left and the bathroom is in front of you. The coffee machine will be on your right and a staff only door to your left.
comment:
The staff is very nice and friendly. You don’t have to pretend to shop. We get so many pregnant people and kids who need a restroom. Just ask the staff for directions if you get turned around in the toys. 

Sometimes the shelves can get pretty close, so navigating a wheel chair or walker isn’t always a straight shot.
